data.description: This house is waiting to welcome you home! The beautiful modern updated kitchen with light gray cabinets, white quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances is spacious and open to the dining area.  This home is very airy with its high ceilings, laminate flooring throughout the whole home, and a large covered and screened in porched to enjoy and BBQ.  It also boasts an oversized yard that is fully fenced and sits on a corner lot.  The owner has taken lots of care to plant many fruit trees that are now flourishing and providing fruits, including bananas, ciruelas, and limes!  Call today to schedule your private showing in person or virtually and fall in love with owning your own piece of Heaven. Conveniently located to all your needs and central between Kissimmee, Davenport, and Haines City!
